ratnāntargatasaṃsthitam iti maṇimadhyastham ||

<commentary>viditaitajjñānasya yogino niṣṭhām āha—jñānāmṛtetyādi | subodham ||</commentary>

idānīṃ vedāntavādino vakṣyamāṇāmnāyakramāgatasya kadācid evaṃ varṇanaṃ syāt | atas tatpratipattyā sukhena tattyāgārthaṃ pūrvārdham āha—atīndriyam ityādi | indriyāṇi parāṇy āhur indriyebhyaḥ paraṃ manaḥ |
